---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Bilingual from '../../components/Bilingual.astro';
import SortVisualizer from '../../components/viz/SortVisualizer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Sorting · CS Notebook">
  <article class="space-y-6">
    <header>
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-cyan mb-2">Algorithms / Sorting</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">
        <Bilingual><span slot="zh">排序算法可视化</span><span slot="en">Sorting Visualizer</span></Bilingual>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh">选择算法与规模，点击播放观察比较与交换过程。柱状图颜色含义：<b class="text-func-amber">黄=比较</b>、<b class="text-func-red">红=交换</b>、<b class="text-func-green">绿=已就位</b>、<b class="text-primary-purple">紫=基准(pivot)</b>。</span>
          <span slot="en">Pick an algorithm and size, then play to watch comparisons and swaps. Colors: <b class="text-func-amber">amber=compare</b>, <b class="text-func-red">red=swap</b>, <b class="text-func-green">green=sorted</b>, <b class="text-primary-purple">purple=pivot</b>.</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </header>

    <SortVisualizer />

    <section class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="glass p-5">
        <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2">
          <Bilingual><span slot="zh">冒泡 / 插入</span><span slot="en">Bubble / Insertion</span></Bilingual>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted">
          <Bilingual>
            <span slot="zh">基础 O(n²) 算法，适合小数组与教学，直观展示相邻比较与逐步归位。</span>
            <span slot="en">Elementary O(n²) algorithms, great for small arrays and teaching — adjacent comparisons, incremental placement.</span>
          </Bilingual>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass p-5">
        <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2">
          <Bilingual><span slot="zh">快排 / 归并</span><span slot="en">Quick / Merge</span></Bilingual>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted">
          <Bilingual>
            <span slot="zh">分治策略，平均 O(n log n)。快排用基准分区，归并稳定地合并有序子段。</span>
            <span slot="en">Divide & conquer, average O(n log n). Quick uses a pivot partition; merge stably merges sorted runs.</span>
          </Bilingual>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
